{"tid":1402180,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【旺角遊行】阮民安認有「行街」　義載「朋友仔」回家：想支持下","createTime":"2019-08-03T15:49:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-03T16:05:09.000Z","uid":66923,"like":26,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"6d12e1c720e3cf593c91cd88b9904041961cc09b","tid":1402180,"uid":66923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T15:49:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3118176/org/40dbe9d2ed70ee4614ba7295139994bc.jpg/8yh3yHSHj6cO7JSyZpvMC0d7RumHz55w161Ic9etSHM?v=w1920r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3118176%2Forg%2F40dbe9d2ed70ee4614ba7295139994bc.jpg%2F8yh3yHSHj6cO7JSyZpvMC0d7RumHz55w161Ic9etSHM%3Fv%3Dw1920r16_9&h=71c9ca15&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《逃犯條例》修訂爭議持續，有示威者在今天（3/8）旺角遊行結束後一度佔領紅隧，到入夜仍然不少示威者在尖沙咀、旺角等地方集結。晚上9點左右，警方開始清場，有不少示威者被捕。有電視台便拍攝到一名疑似Ekids成員阮民安（Tommy）的男子亦身處旺角，網友見此便擷取畫面放到社交平台分享，笑指這位疑似Tommy太過亮眼：「已經唔係督唔督灰嘅Level。」引來大批網友讚好。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3118170/org/d3d6ae591fe06c93d247634ee2719c5a.jpg/5bsjViKwZwsTfucmsrm1Endo10cU9iYmsEtYfrBLWH4?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3118170%2Forg%2Fd3d6ae591fe06c93d247634ee2719c5a.jpg%2F5bsjViKwZwsTfucmsrm1Endo10cU9iYmsEtYfrBLWH4%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=9dce228c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nTommy接受《香港01》訪問時便直認相中的銀髮男是他本人，剛剛載完兩位「朋友仔」離開旺角，現正準備回家，：「係我嚟嘅！我啱啱喺旺角行街，所以就了解下個情況咁。（你見到個情況係點？）氣氛好緊張，好多細我哋好多嘅後生仔做緊啲嘢，好有經驗咁。（咁多後生仔會唔會好心痛？）會，因為我自己都有小朋友，都想將正確思想灌輸畀小朋友，所以去咗啲地方行街，支持一下。」他又指自己星期一都會響應「三罷」行動，到旺角麥花臣集會：「今日我老婆都以全職媽媽身份同我請假，我好支持佢，因為而家已經唔係政治問題，而係良知問題。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3118251/org/51070b3a23886ebc666b223311827522.JPG/2eDWjs7A38ifwIXA9NN5EOa32_5aTj2vHzGvyh8xr8o?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3118251%2Forg%2F51070b3a23886ebc666b223311827522.JPG%2F2eDWjs7A38ifwIXA9NN5EOa32_5aTj2vHzGvyh8xr8o%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=b1a8474e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n阮民安批准老婆張倚雯（Eva）8月5日罷工。（Facebook/@Tommy Man On Yuen）"},{"pid":"1e995930656be372956834afec35f51c7e699d42","tid":1402180,"uid":76632,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T15:50:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/33w3rcY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F33w3rcY.jpg&h=04db1119&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n舊相回帶，踩唔死我"},{"pid":"58959940fa297c20a017a299d3d65385a7d0d51a","tid":1402180,"uid":40272,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T15:51:11.000Z","msg":"唔笑佢地會考加埋既分數"},{"pid":"852ad5dbd2c55fa1edcb549daf9fc2519231c8d7","tid":1402180,"uid":5445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6d12e1c720e3cf593c91cd88b9904041961cc09b","tid":1402180,"uid":66923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T15:49:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3118176/org/40dbe9d2ed70ee4614ba7295139994bc.jpg/8yh3yHSHj6cO7JSyZpvMC0d7RumHz55w161Ic9etSHM?v=w1920r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3118176%2Forg%2F40dbe9d2ed70ee4614ba7295139994bc.jpg%2F8yh3yHSHj6cO7JSyZpvMC0d7RumHz55w161Ic9etSHM%3Fv%3Dw1920r16_9&h=71c9ca15&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《逃犯條例》修訂爭議持續，有示威者在今天（3/8）旺角遊行結束後一度佔領紅隧，到入夜仍然不少示威者在尖沙咀、旺角等地方集結。晚上9點左右，警方開始清場，有不少示威者被捕。有電視台便拍攝到一名疑似Ekids成員阮民安（Tommy）的男子亦身處旺角，網友見此便擷取畫面放到社交平台分享，笑指這位疑似Tommy太過亮眼：「已經唔係督唔督灰嘅Level。」引來大批網友讚好。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3118170/org/d3d6ae591fe06c93d247634ee2719c5a.jpg/5bsjViKwZwsTfucmsrm1Endo10cU9iYmsEtYfrBLWH4?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3118170%2Forg%2Fd3d6ae591fe06c93d247634ee2719c5a.jpg%2F5bsjViKwZwsTfucmsrm1Endo10cU9iYmsEtYfrBLWH4%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=9dce228c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nTommy接受《香港01》訪問時便直認相中的銀髮男是他本人，剛剛載完兩位「朋友仔」離開旺角，現正準備回家，：「係我嚟嘅！我啱啱喺旺角行街，所以就了解下個情況咁。（你見到個情況係點？）氣氛好緊張，好多細我哋好多嘅後生仔做緊啲嘢，好有經驗咁。（咁多後生仔會唔會好心痛？）